oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Willis Brothers Fact Sheet
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Offset printing; Willis Brothers;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A black and white negative taped to and framed by a masking sheet advertising facts about the Willis Brothers (Guy, Skeeter, and Vic), including songs recorded, albums recorded, movies and television shows they appeared on, record label, and countries visited. The negative would have been used to create a corresponding printing plate.
